(802, 1, '2015-12-10 22:47:17', '2015-12-10 22:47:17', 'INITIATIVE\n\n“Momma said: There is only so much fortune a man really needs- and the rest is for showin’ off”\n-Forrest Gump\n\nWe are a small company. Fueled by a few curious individuals who want to procure beautiful eyewear in a way that hasn’t been done before.\n\nWe believe in having a sustainable business, with a portion set aside to effect whatever change is within our reach. Our ambition is not to constantly reshape the bottom line and increase profits; but to effect change in our industry with out work and outside of it with our initiative.\n\nYour one pair of DIROCCO’s helps restore the sight of one person who has become blind through cataracts. So enjoy your DIROCCO’s and thank you for helping us restore the gift of sight.', 'Initative', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-10 22:47:17', '2015-12-10 22:47:17', '', 127, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/127-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
